dxsportcom  china dongxiang group co ltd  about us  company overview china dongxiang group co ltd china dongxiang or the company stock code  together with its subsidiaries the group is a leading international sportswear brand enterprise based in china the group is primarily engaged in the design development marketing and wholesaling of branded sportswear in china since  may  china dongxiang has owned all rights to the internationally recognised kappa brand in the prc and macau in april  as a new chapter in its multibranding strategy china dongxiang announced the acquisition of phenix co ltdphenix which mainly owned and managed kappa and phenix brands in japan as a result china dongxiang is enriching its regional brand portfolio and extending product types to help develop the china ski and outdoor fashion markets the companys aim is also to further enhance its current rd techniques and ability to integrate japan phenixs strong design and rd capacity as well as relevant talents ultimately they want to provide a solid platform for kappa and other brands longterm development in china these days china dongxiangs major products convey an active fashionable and youthful image and are warmly welcomed by chinas fast growing affluent consumers   china market  kappa brand history first established in  the kappa brand started to garner market recognition in europe during the s and s and before long became one of the most renowned names for casual sportswear in europe since then the world has been enchanted by the lifestyle represented by kappa products so vividly identified by omini its unique logo featuring a backtoback couple through china dongxiang the group kappa landed in china in  to embark on an amazing journey of phenomenal growth in this populous nation in may  the group acquired the brand ownership of kappa in mainland china and macau to secure complete autonomy in all aspects of the brands operations in these markets such as product development marketing sales organizations and channel strategy allowing it to devise comprehensive marketoriented development plans in april the group secured the entire interests of kappa in mainland china macau and japan following its acquisition of phenix then owner of the kappa brand and phenix brand in japan brand positioning after more than a decade of soulsearching and development efforts kappa has further cemented its strong foundation in china today kappa continues to carry that unmistakable sporting gene but on top of that it has positioned itself as a brand for the fashionable sportive lifestyle with the concept of rebellious passionate and outgoing it targets young consumers who are enthusiastic about pop culture discerning about the quality of life eager to explore new ideas and happy to show off their personalities brand products it requires rigorous practices in product quality and design to give substance to the concept of rebellious passionate and outgoing kappa products are developed on the basis of various aspects in pop culture on top of the basic sporting gene a diverse range of trendy elements are incorporated in the designs in addition more emphasis has been put on consumers experience and the creation of overall styles through product matching in order to develop unique infashion products that meet the aesthetic standards and demands of the trendy brand marketing kappa is unique also in its marketing approach which seeks to promote the pop culture and shape the trendy lifestyle more emphasis has been put in promoting the brand in the dimension of pop culture through indepth crossovers with the entertainment music and art professions so that pop culture is seamlessly blended into the products and their marketing sales network kappa retail stores including selfowned and distributors stores cover all major regions and cities in china with the ongoing promotion of the brand new image of our retail stores consumers are set to experience the rebellious outgoing and character of kappa in all aspects from products to shop display in future while persisting in innovation the group will also optimize the distribution of its channels within its stable and existing sales network in order to continuously enhance the business performance of retail stores and drive the kappa brand to new heights in view of the growing maturity of the ecommerce market the group continued to develop and optimize its ecommerce channel through the development of special online products the sales mix of online products has been optimized while our product and brand reputation has also been gradually enhanced as a result promotion and festive events were also organized in association with ecommerce partners to further explore the market and appeal to more consumers japan market  phenix brand positioning in  phenix was established by mr tajima kazuo an outdoor sporting enthusiast and quickly earned high praise and widespread fame in skiing alpinism gliding and kayaking mr tajima devoted his whole life to his favorite outdoor sports at which he not only excelled but also gave his best efforts to help those who loved them too phenix dna brings together all his ideas and passes them on from generation to generation like its founder the phenix company itself has been deeply devoted to all extreme outdoor sports including skiing and hopes to provide the finest support for outdoor sports enthusiasts through its fine line of products the companys technical rd centre with over  years history has professional development techniques for creating advanced sportswear based on years of research into sports dynamics and physiology over the years year this knowledge has been applied to a wide range of functional materials to meet the demands of leading athletes across the world phenix revels in the joys of sporting competition how to extend techniques and function to aid sports is the dna of phenix which has been passed down until now as taught through mr tajimas words and deeds combining function that provides the body with comfort and protection as well as a fashion sense that makes people feel stylish and happy results in the creative idea of feasting on sports this is how phenix has opened up a brand new world product introduction phenix owns a number of popular brands such as phenix xnix inhabitant and kappa which have been widely hailed by consumers phenix as an international top brand within the industry phenix focuses closely on product function and fashion seeking perfection in every detail function and fashion blend beneath simple designs and beautiful shapes the wide application of functional materials allows phenix to respond quickly to environmental changes during different seasons the result is excellent resistance to cold even in freezing conditions with phenix we can see the detailoriented mindset of the japanese and the rd philosophy of emplying the designs of other products and industries these products are more than just outdoor gear they represent apparel that reflects todays fashion trends xnix xnix is a snowboarding apparel brand that has rapidly grown in popularity created by fusing function and fashion the brand includes various styles of gear and accessories multiple tests with the full support and cooperation of top snowboarders this professional brand offers excellent water resistance flexibility and heat preservation which allows for greater snowboarding enjoyment under any weather conditions inhabitant inhabitant literally means aborigines which is an apparel brand mainly for young people covering almost all extreme sports like surfing snowboarding wakeboarding unleashed bmx and skateboarding as well as entertainment and lifestyle activities like djing just as the name name implies inhabitant includes the individual spirit and passion of x generation that is we are all inhabitants inhabitant commits itself to constantly providing aborigines with various unique and fashionable sportswear and regular apparel such as diving suits and snowboard suits made of high performance materials as well as casual sportswear made of renewable cotton and sweatreleasing materials kappa since launched in japan in  kappa has been focusing on sports and committing to provide people who enjoy sports with fashion and comfort during sports it is what kappa has focused for a long time to sense every athletes hot breath to subtly detect any change of their facial expression to correctly respond to the climatic and environmental changes where they are and to extend a maximum presentation of their healthy and energetic moment as well as their personality the spirit and passion in athletes are the power promoting kappa to achieve continuous progress and development in  phenix company bought all rights of kappa in japan so that phenixs philosophy based on sports obtained a better development and extension currently products of kappa japan include collections of athletics casual and golf distribution network currently sales outlets are located at popular skiing areas in japan korea australia europe canada and united states marketing and promotion sponsoring professional skiers and teams is the major marketing and promotion strategy of phenix which was appointed the official supplier of the japan national ski team at the  vancouver winter olympics moreover the norwegian alpine ski team and many excellent japanese skiers including akira sasaki seika matsuzawa daisuke sasaki and yasuko kono all sponsored by the phenix brand while top skiers like daisuke murakami katsufumi matsui daniel frank zi fujinuma keiko inamura qiki tosaki kohei kawaguchi and takayuki fujiwara and others have long been sponsored by xnix back to top  copyright china dongxiang group co ltd all rights reserveddisclaimerprivacysitemap chen yihong china dongxiang group co ltd profile  biography  bloomberg feedback chen yihong chairmanceoexec dir china dongxiang group co ltd career history chairmanceoexec dir china dongxiang group co ltd present own